==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Bertillon system
<hw>Ber`til`lon" sys"tem</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[After Alphonse
<ets>Bertillon</ets>, French anthropologist.]</ety> <def>A system for
the identification of persons by a physical description based upon
anthropometric measurements, notes of markings, deformities, color,
impression of thumb lines, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bertram</ent>⟦br⟧
